          <a href="/concepts/atman" class="tag">真我/Atman</a>
          <a href="/concepts/jnana" class="tag">参究法</a>
          <a href="/concepts/jnana" class="tag">修行/Sadhana</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <p>拉玛那马哈希Space | 传承自印度阿鲁那佳拉圣山</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
